&lt;h1 id="aws-s3和hexo">AWS S3和Hexo&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>1.安装插件&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-powershell" data-lang="powershell">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e"># 装置&lt;/span>
