&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>2.改&lt;code>_config.yml&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-powershell" data-lang="powershell">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>deploy&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">:&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e"># - type: &amp;#39;git&amp;#39;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e"># repo: git@github.com:aaaaaaanthony/aaaaaaanthony.github.io.git&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e"># branch: master&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> type&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">:&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;aws-s3&amp;#39;&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#75715e"># 写死&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> region&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">:&lt;/span> ap-east-&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">1&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#75715e"># 区域名&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> bucket&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">:&lt;/span> mmzcg.com &lt;span style="color:#75715e"># 桶名&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>如果要部署多个地方,每个仓库的type前面要加一个&lt;code>-&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>如果只有一个,就只用type开头就行&lt;/p>
&lt;p>3.执行环境变量&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>export AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID&lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span>AKIA2Q6ZSIPP7MKZOFHR
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>export AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY&lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span>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
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>source /etc/profile
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>4.部署&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>hexo clean
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>hexo algoli
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>hexo d -g
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>发现报错，&lt;code>The bucket does not allow ACLs&lt;/code>，还需要在存储中开启 &lt;code>ACLs&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
