&lt;h2 id="快照导出到s3">快照导出到S3&lt;/h2>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://docs.aws.amazon.com/zh_cn/AmazonRDS/latest/UserGuide/USER_ExportSnapshot.html#USER_ExportSnapshot.Exporting">参考文档&lt;/a>&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>
